{"tid":487370,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來分手並唔係最痛","createTime":"2017-12-02T16:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T09:45:28.000Z","uid":153648,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3c4ede4a59b6bead080eeaffcb1cf2bff6f42ddf","tid":487370,"uid":153648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:44:57.000Z","msg":"分咗手差唔多一個月<br />\n開頭話未玩夠而分手<br />\n我想等，等到佢玩夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分手後幾日發現佢同返ex聯絡 (fb add fd+ig follow)<br />\n一齊嗰陣已經成日當佢係假想敵<br />\n<br />\n而家諗到佢地有機會復合<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(佢ex啱啱離婚+生咗仔，唔知會唔會真係幫人養便宜仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n個心痛到飛起，心如刀割#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如一槍打死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：一齊咗3年半"},{"pid":"fa0c4131c6b52b248ae46b3e0d667eb0ef0dce77","tid":487370,"uid":142725,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"當佢係臭雞就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好自貶身價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14c951ebf0425d1c3f3e462e5adfa10ffb040ec","tid":487370,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:47:29.000Z","msg":"人妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cea1bdec132219a2f9c28b230b861f880ee43b5","tid":487370,"uid":153648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當佢係臭雞就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好自貶身價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放唔低，真係好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但點解明知我最怕佢ex都要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18dd0ea2221136